        <div class="collapsible-header active"><i class="material-icons">live_help</i>Tutorial</div>
        <div class="collapsible-body"><p>You are in control of the Zybourne Clock, a futuristic device that allows you to change history. Note that the timeline can only hold 4 events at a time, so in order to insert in a new event into the timeline, you have to delete a event first. <em>Good luck!</em></p></div>
