        <div class="collapsible-header"><i class="material-icons">warning</i>The Lore</div>
        <div class="collapsible-body"><p>You are Sylus, an R&D scientist working for the Commonwealth of Rasenni. The evil dictator 'Johnny Five-Ace' has destroyed our country in a great war, leaving you as a bitter war veteran. Luckily, you discovered a device called the Zybourne Clock within the ruins of the Civilus Primiscotas. Johnny once used this Clock to help him win the great war. <br><br> Now, it's time to use the Clock's power against Johnny. Change history to stop Johnny Five-Ace from winning (while also ensuring humanity doesn't die in the process).</p></div>
